.SH "WARNINGS"
.sp
In order to compile a program containing these functions in \fIfile.c\fP
it is necessary to use: \f(CRcc \fIfile.c\fP \-lplot3\fP
.sp
\fIColor\fP specification and three\-dimensional primitives are BRL
extensions to the "unix plot" language that are not generally found on
other systems.
